data.text:
This is an annotated list of databases produced by Connecticut state agencies. It was last checked for broken links on August 26, 2024.

To return to the State Agency Databases Project home page, click here.

As of August 2020, we were unable to locate publicly searchable databases produced by a Connecticut state agency in these areas:

Science & Technology

If you know of Connecticut-produced databases in these or other subjects shown here, please use the "email me" link in the Documents Specialist box above to drop us a line.
